To install Wiki Wide Web, the following steps are needed:

1). Configure the lib/db.class.php mysql settings to reflect your setup
2). Modify the tools/createdb.sql with your admin username, password hash and email
3). Run the creatdb.sql on the database server to setup the initial database
4). Ensure the cache directory is writable by the web server
5). Modify tools/wikiwideweb/defaults/preferences/makePrefs.js to point to your server
6). Build the firefox extension in tools using the Makefile
7). Fix all the bugs that crop up